-- Author Satyajit Das Discusses Currency Wars (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-05-28T12:18:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-28/author-satyajit-das-discusses-currency-wars-audio-.html
Satyajit Das, a risk consultant and 
author of "Extreme Money: The Masters of the Universe and the 
Cult of Risk," explains that some countries' monetary policies 
can devalue their currency. Das talks with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox 
and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:38
 